Alembic — database migrations (async, single database)

The DB URL and SSL come from callup.config.settings (see alembic/env.py); they are NOT
read from alembic.ini. Use the Supabase Direct or Session pooler connection (port 5432),
never the Transaction pooler (6543). Every autogenerated migration must be reviewed before
it is applied.

Commands (run from backend/):
  uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "<message>"   # generate, then review the file
  uv run alembic upgrade head                              # apply
  uv run alembic upgrade head --sql                        # render SQL offline (no DB write)
  uv run alembic downgrade -1                              # roll back one revision
  uv run alembic current / history                         # inspect state

