    recruiter.email unique, application unique(candidate_id, job_posting_id), ON DELETE
    CASCADE on candidate-child FKs, and the deferred org.owner_recruiter_id circular FK
    (fk_org_owner_recruiter, created via ALTER after both tables exist).
    Deferred to later phases: pgvector embeddings, Dice ingestion fields, fitment scores,
    a normalized contacts table, the apply-session state machine, and a separate outreach
    record.
